                        <interp inst="t18411129-name-184" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH BROWN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a waiter, and live in Chicksand-street, Brick-lane. At half-past seven o'clock, in the morning of the 17th of Novem<lb></lb>ber, I was at the picture-shop, at the corner of Cornhill—the policeman came up and showed me my handkerchief—I felt, and it was gone—this now produced is it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
